歲人士<br />\n- 香港永久性居民<br />\n- 持有效學生證<br />\n如何計算利息<br />\n<br />\n- uFinance秒貸零用錢不收取利息，一個月內任何時間隨時可以還款。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">- 如果過期，未能在一個月內還款，uFinance會收取每個月港幣5元的手續費。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所需文件<br />\n<br />\n- 香港身分證副本<br />\n- 學生證副本<br />\n- 住址證明副本<br />\n- 銀行月結單副本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貸款最高額度<br />\n<br />\n- 額度會隨著用戶於uFinance成功借貸次數所增加<br />\n- 首次使用$500<br />\n- 最高限額為$1500"},{"pid":"552639505491ccf482bfd04206ef20ef44f58a3c","tid":183567,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab41d41ff4a809920e4bcd30402bc331cd93cb5b","tid":183567,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:17:14.000Z","msg":"咁似上年套日劇，錢的戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n借小d，人地還錢容易，走數風險細，個息仲可以拉到好高，係搵人收麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e84c658862d1a6d4558b82563e629c7117f217","tid":183567,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fb0a176dd49ae8e9dccb0de1c3def5545c6fc681","tid":183567,"uid":102134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除500元貸款，Ufinance亦提供一般大學生貸款，黎子謙舉例有從事時裝設計、電影製作學生，因應「做好個Project」而有資金需要，向Ufinance借兩萬，分24個月還，<span style=\"color: red;\">年利率介乎11至12厘，比起一般信用卡貸款30厘為低。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行咪仲低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻仔先借 11厘喎</blockquote><br />\n冇收入證明借條柒</blockquote><br />\n冇入息  仲要個人貸款  11厘息算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44071765f56df641e